  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionSelectionDialog
    Dialog that asks the user to choose an action among the ones passed to the constructor.
    AmmoSelectionDialog
    Dialog that asks the user to choose an ammo or power up among the ones passed to the constructor.
    DisconnectionDialog
    A simple popup window notifying the user that the server connection is lost.
    GameResultsDialog
    A window that displays the game results object passed to the constructor.
    PaymentSelectionDialog
    Dialog that asks the use to choose how to pay, by choosing among the resources that are passed to the constructor.
    PlayerEquipDialog
    Popup window showing the weapons and power up cards owned by a user.
    PowerUpSelectionDialog
    Dialog that makes the user choose among the power ups whose IDs are passed to the constructor.
    WeaponSelectionDialog
    Dialog that makes the user choose among the weapons whose IDs are passed to the constructor.
